OL,3,C'People are living in garden sheds':
OL,4,CThe reality of the housing crisis
OL,6,FHigh demand and low supply means the
OL,7,Fcompetition to rent a home across the
OL,8,FChannel Islands is worsening as
OL,9,Fproperties are snapped up within 24
OL,10,Fhours of being listed.
OL,12,FConcerns are growing with one Guernsey
OL,13,Festate agent saying that people are
OL,14,Fnow "living in garden sheds" due to
OL,15,Fthe lack of other options.
