OL,3,C'People are living in garden sheds':
OL,4,CThe reality of the housing crisis
OL,6,FMadvi Harchad adds: "I was three, four
OL,7,Fmonths pregnant and we needed a bigger
OL,8,Fplace for our baby, it was stressful."
OL,10,FDeputy John Gollop believes Guernsey
OL,11,FStates needs to take action to support
OL,12,Fboth prospective tenants and landlords.
OL,14,FHe says: "I would like to see some of
OL,15,Fthe incentives that used to apply to
OL,16,Flandlords reintroduced, the tax
OL,17,Fpackage they had a few years ago was
OL,18,Fperhaps more convenient than today."
