OL,3,C'People are living in garden sheds':
OL,4,CThe reality of the housing crisis
OL,6,FDeputy Gollop has previously called
OL,7,Ffor politicians to prioritise fixing
OL,8,Fthe island's property crisis and wants
OL,9,Fnew ideas to improve social housing
OL,10,Fand help young couples.
OL,12,FFirst addressing Madvi's experience, I
OL,13,Funderstand it is illegal for Guernsey
OL,14,Flandlords to discriminate against
OL,15,Fsomeone with children but barely
OL,16,Fanyone has been taken to court for it.
