OL,3,C'People are living in garden sheds':
OL,4,CThe reality of the housing crisis
OL,6,FLooking at the wider property market
OL,7,Fthe real issue is supply - homes in
OL,8,FGuernsey receive an average of 50 to
OL,9,F100 applications when they're first
OL,10,Flisted and they're usually snapped up
OL,11,Fwithin 24 hours to 48 hours.
OL,13,FThey are building more key worker
OL,14,Faccommodation but I am constantly
OL,15,Fhearing complaints from people who say
OL,16,Fit is just too expensive.
OL,18,FThe average rent for a single person
OL,19,Fin Guernsey is now around #1,500, much
OL,20,Fhigher than in parts of the UK where
OL,21,Fyou can rent a whole house for that.
