OL,3,C'People are living in garden sheds':
OL,4,CThe reality of the housing crisis
OL,6,FIn Jersey, they are building lots of
OL,7,Fone-bedroom flats but hardly anything
OL,8,Ffor families.
OL,10,FEven though Jersey and Guernsey have
OL,11,Fvery similar problems, there is barely
OL,12,Fany collaborative work happening
OL,13,Fbetween politicians in both islands to
OL,14,Ftry and solve this crisis.
OL,16,FJersey's Housing Minister to my
OL,17,Fknowledge has never even met with his
OL,18,FGuernsey counterpart to discuss this.
