OL,3,C'People are living in garden sheds':
OL,4,CThe reality of the housing crisis
OL,6,FThere is a lot of talk by politicians
OL,7,Fbut what is needed now is action and
OL,8,Funtil they come up with something, the
OL,9,Freality is that more and more people
OL,10,Fwill leave the Channel Islands because
OL,11,Fthere just isn't enough housing that's
OL,12,Faffordable and suitable enough for
OL,13,Fthem to live in.
